Package gnu.x11.tk Description

Provide a X toolkit.

This package is _not_ ready yet. We are still in prototype stage. Our goal is to provide a modern look-and-feel interface such as Swing. For brain-stormers, please check this official guideline.

Please ignore any java classes in this package for now. They are highly experimental.
